The paper deals with information retrieval and coding theory, which are both related to the field of information theory (cs.IT). The paper also discusses privacy and security concerns (cs.CR), as well as the implementation complexity of linear schemes (cs.DS). The use of a database and servers suggests a connection to database systems (cs.DB), and the design of a capacity-achieving scheme involves optimization and algorithms (cs.CC).
